---
---

<section class="s-white" style="padding:140px 0 100px;">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="auth-header reveal">
      <p class="section-label" style="margin-bottom:16px">Über uns</p>
      <h2 class="auth-h2">
        800 Deals. 150 Einheiten.
        <br/><em class="italic-gradient">Und selbst bei uns lag Geld auf dem Tisch.</em>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="auth-grid">
      <div class="auth-text reveal-left">
        <p class="auth-body">
          Julian und ich besitzen selbst über 150 Einheiten. Als wir unsere eigenen
          Portfolios durchgerechnet haben, war das ein Schock. Genau deshalb haben
          wir ImmoIQ gebaut — damit kein Immobilienbesitzer mehr Geld auf dem Tisch
          liegen lässt.
        </p>
        <div class="auth-author">
          <div class="auth-avatar">MB</div>
          <div>
            <p class="auth-name">Max Bertlein</p>
            <p class="auth-role">Gründer, WBD Gruppe</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="auth-badges">
          <span class="auth-badge">📺 Amazon Prime „The Mittelstand"</span>
          <span class="auth-badge">🏢 WBD Gruppe</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="auth-stats reveal-right">
        <div class="auth-stat">
          <span class="auth-stat-val">800+</span>
          <span class="auth-stat-label">Deals begleitet</span>
        </div>
        <div class="auth-stat">
          <span class="auth-stat-val">300M€</span>
          <span class="auth-stat-label">Transaktionsvolumen</span>
        </div>
        <div class="auth-stat">
          <span class="auth-stat-val">150+</span>
          <span class="auth-stat-label">Eigene Einheiten</span>
        </div>
        <div class="auth-stat">
          <span class="auth-stat-val">12k€</span>
          <span class="auth-stat-label">Gespart — 1. Testkunde</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .auth-header { margin-bottom: 64px; }
  .auth-h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4.5vw, 48px); line-height: 1.1; margin: 0; }
  .auth-h2 em { /* styled via .italic-gradient */ }

  .auth-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 56px; }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { .auth-grid { grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr; gap: 80px; } }

  .auth-body { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 32px; }

  .auth-author { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .auth-avatar {
    width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--text); color: #fff;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700;
  }
  .auth-name { font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; margin: 0; }
  .auth-role { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0; }

  .auth-badges { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; }
  .auth-badge {
    padding: 10px 16px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500;
    background: var(--light); border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .auth-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }
  .auth-stat {
    padding: 32px; border-radius: 16px;
    background: var(--light);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .auth-stat-val {
    display: block; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-weight: 700; font-size: 32px; color: var(--text);
  }
  .auth-stat-label {
    display: block; margin-top: 6px;
    color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 13px;
  }
</style>
